	   <tr><td colspan=2>Pets make great targets!!&nbsp;&nbsp;I spent roughly 2-3 hours at a time at newb log in Nektulos casting Ward undead on my flimsy pet and worked up my skill.  I trained only 5 points guild wise and cast the rest.  Ok maybe there are a lot of Decaying skells and Skells in Nek but at lvl 22 with a descent weap, 2 hits with weap and 1 ward undead kills skells.  Take the hits too, watch your timing and cast away, I got my evoc to 105 in a few days while collecting bone chips and HQ bear pelts.  Only costs some time from Hard playing.<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Tue Feb 19 12:02:02 2002</em><br>&nbsp;<br>Saelelen Slipshade<br>Dark Elf Shadow Knight<br>Custos Cogitatum</td></tr>
