	   <tr><td colspan=2>I may have missed the mark on this, but it sounds to me like you mean training from your guild master. First, do not do that. You have a pet. Summon one, and tell it to stand still while you merrily cast ward undead on it. It'll develop a cute little glowing blue halo, and ignore the fact that it's being warded (you can't attack your pet). Do this until your evocation is maxed, and you should be fine casting whichever version of the spell line that you currently have.<br>&nbsp;<br>Phirean Ycze<br><br>Test</td></tr>
